short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dirt Bike wallpaper turn new tab to custom HD Dirt Bike background. Dirt Bike wallpaper background theme for fans.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension Features:

1. Enjoy a new Dirt Bike wallpaper each time you open a new tab.  
2. Randomize the Dirt Bike background or mark your favorites in the wallpaper selection panel.  
3. Use the search bar to get results from your preferred search engine.  
4. Quickly access your emails and social media accounts.  
5. Automatically display the current date and time.  
6. Take notes with the "New Note" feature to keep track of your tasks.  
7. Easily access your most visited websites.  
8. Conveniently access your bookmarks.  
9. Add websites to the Shortcut panel for quick access.  
10. Quickly navigate to Google apps.  
11. Explore more themes with a single click.  
12. Share content easily on social media.  
13. Download wallpapers directly with quick access.  
14. Quick access to play games.  
15. Enable fun animations like snow, rain, falling leaves, or fireworks in the Dirt Bike new tab.
